<reference id="lcArea" xml:lang="en-us">
  <title><xmlelement>lcArea</xmlelement></title>
  <shortdesc rev="DITA1.3 proposal-13106">A <xmlelement>lcArea</xmlelement> was deprecated in DITA
    version 1.3. It was replaced with the <xmlelement>lcArea2</xmlelement> element. It was originally
    intended to define an area of a hotspot image that contains a correct or incorrect choice in a
    hotspot assessment interaction.</shortdesc>
